sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / KFP SDK
    participant UI as Frontend UI<br/>3000/TCP HTTP
    participant API as API Server<br/>8888/TCP REST<br/>8887/TCP gRPC
    participant DB as MySQL/PostgreSQL<br/>3306/5432 TCP
    participant ObjStore as MinIO / S3<br/>9000/443 TCP
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Argo as Argo Workflows
    participant Cache as Cache Server<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Driver as Driver<br/>(init container)
    participant MLMD as ML Metadata<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant Launcher as Launcher<br/>(sidecar)
    participant UserCode as User Container
    participant PA as Persistence Agent
    participant SWC as Scheduled WF Controller

    Note over User,SWC: Flow 1: Pipeline Run Execution

    User->>API: POST /apis/v2beta1/runs<br/>Bearer Token
    API->>DB: Store run record<br/>Username/Password
    API->>ObjStore: Store pipeline spec<br/>Access Key/Secret
    API->>K8s: Create Argo Workflow<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8s->>Argo: Schedule Workflow

    Argo->>Driver: Run init container
    Driver->>MLMD: Query upstream outputs<br/>gRPC/8080
    Driver->>API: Cache check<br/>gRPC/8887 SA Token

    alt Cache Miss
        Driver->>Launcher: Pod spec patch (proceed)
        Launcher->>UserCode: Execute user command
        UserCode-->>Launcher: Output artifacts
        Launcher->>ObjStore: Upload artifacts<br/>Access Key/Secret
        Launcher->>MLMD: Publish results<br/>gRPC/8080
    else Cache Hit
        Driver->>K8s: Mark step cached (skip execution)
    end

    PA->>K8s: Watch Workflow status<br/>SA Token
    PA->>API: Report workflow state<br/>gRPC/8887 Projected SA Token

    Note over User,SWC: Flow 2: Cache Hit (Webhook Path)

    K8s->>Cache: MutatingWebhook on pod create<br/>HTTPS/8443 TLS
    Cache->>DB: Lookup cache entry<br/>Username/Password
    Cache-->>K8s: JSON Patch (replace container with busybox)

    Note over User,SWC: Flow 3: Scheduled Pipeline Execution

    K8s->>SWC: ScheduledWorkflow informer<br/>HTTPS/443 SA Token
    SWC->>API: CreateRun<br/>gRPC/8887 Projected SA Token
    SWC->>K8s: Update ScheduledWorkflow status<br/>HTTPS/443 SA Token
